data.description: This is your opportunity to own a spacious 4 bedroom, 2 1/2 car garage Twin home at the end of a cul-de-sac,  that offers a fenced and oversized rear yard, a deck with covered porch and so much more.  Living and dining room offer newer flooring off of a ceramic tile foyer at front door,  20-foot long  kitchen with potential for a gourmet enthusiast chef's dream.   4 generous size bedrooms with walk-in closets and ceiling fans. Full ceramic hall bath, and a full primary bath with shower.  The lower level office is partially finished with access to huge 2-car garage. To round it off there is a spacious irregular yard with some privacy and a large concrete patio in rear.  SHOWINGS START at Open House Sunday 11/19/123 1:00 to 3:00 PM
